N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 25.11 - Competitive class

State Regulations

The competitive class shall include all
positions for which the Chief Administrator of the Courts finds it is
practicable to determine the merit and fitness of applicants by competitive
examination. Notes
